<plot>Sai Kung Story is a series of three vignettes set in Sai Kung. In the first, a village girl dreaming of going away to the city as a model clashes with a fashion designer who has dropped by her village for inspiration. In the second, a young slacker postman who sends letters to a girl from her boyfriend in France falls for her. In the last, a widow must consider whether to accept the love of her dead husband's best friend, as she toils away in her in-law's eatery house.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?473923</url></doc>
